channel.title: Looking For a running server to invest in / buy
channel.description: Hey guys long story short I am looking for a server to invest my time and money into, I haven't the time to start a new server from scratch but I do enjoy being involved in succeeding / potential servers, money is not a problem (to a limit) and yeah basically please inbox me a contact method for you (Msn preferred) and I will get hold of you, also if there is none found or I find a good potential server I am considering buying.
